---
// CTA Final FINAL - cor roxo #8B5CF6 consistente, fade-in
---

<section class="py-[6rem] bg-white border-t border-[#E5E5E5] fade-section">
  <div class="max-w-[40rem] mx-auto px-[1rem] md:px-[1.5rem] text-center">
    
    <h2 class="text-[2rem] sm:text-[2.5rem] font-semibold text-[#0A0A0A] mb-[1rem]">
      Pronto para simplificar?
    </h2>
    
    <p class="text-[1.125rem] text-[#737373] mb-[2rem]">
      Veja uma demonstração ou comece gratuitamente.
    </p>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-[1rem] mb-[2rem]">
      <button 
        onclick="openModal()"
        class="px-[2rem] py-[1rem] bg-[#6D28D9] hover:bg-[#5B21B6] text-white font-medium rounded-full transition-all duration-200 cursor-pointer"
      >
        Agendar demonstração
      </button>
      <a 
        href="https://wikimee.app/signup"
        class="px-[2rem] py-[1rem] text-[#0A0A0A] font-medium border border-[#E5E5E5] rounded-full hover:border-[#D4D4D4] hover:bg-[#FAFAFA] transition-all duration-200"
      >
        Começar gratuitamente
      </a>
    </div>
    
    <p class="text-[0.875rem] text-[#A3A3A3]">
      Sem cartão de crédito. Setup em 5 minutos.
    </p>
    
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .fade-section {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(2rem);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;
  }
  
  .fade-section.is-visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
</style>
